<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>자주 묻는 질문</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

    <style>
        .accordion-content {
            overflow: hidden;
            max-height: 0;
            transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out;
        }

        .accordion-content.open {
            max-height: 1000px;
            /* 충분히 큰 값으로 설정 */
        }

        .icon-radix {
            transform: rotate(0deg);
            /* 닫혀 있을 때 ^ 표시로 변경 */
        }

        .icon-open {
            transform: rotate(180deg);
            /* 열려 있을 때 ^ 표시로 변경 */
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
        <div class="container px-4 md:px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="space-y-4 text-center">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl">자주 묻는 질문</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-[600px] mx-auto">
                    궁금한 점이 있나요? 아래 자주 묻는 질문을 확인해보세요.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-12 space-y-4">
                <div data-orientation="vertical">
                    <div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b">
                        <h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex">
                            <button type="button" aria-controls="radix-1" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"
                                data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-button-1"
                                class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between py-4 transition-all hover:underline text-base font-medium"
                                onclick="toggleAccordion('radix-1')">
                                제품 배송은 얼마나 걸리나요?
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200 icon-radix">
                                    <path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                        </h3>
                        <div data-state="closed" id="radix-1" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-button-1"
                            data-orientation="vertical" class="accordion-content text-sm">
                            <p class="py-4">제품 배송은 보통 3-5일 정도 소요됩니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b">
                        <h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex">
                            <button type="button" aria-controls="radix-2" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"
                                data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-button-2"
                                class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between py-4 transition-all hover:underline text-base font-medium"
                                onclick="toggleAccordion('radix-2')">
                                반품 및 환불 정책은 어떻게 되나요?
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200 icon-radix">
                                    <path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                        </h3>
                        <div data-state="closed" id="radix-2" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-button-2"
                            data-orientation="vertical" class="accordion-content text-sm">
                            <p class="py-4">반품 및 환불은 제품 수령 후 7일 이내에 가능합니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b">
                        <h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex">
                            <button type="button" aria-controls="radix-3" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"
                                data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-button-3"
                                class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between py-4 transition-all hover:underline text-base font-medium"
                                onclick="toggleAccordion('radix-3')">
                                제품 A와 제품 B의 차이점은 무엇인가요?
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200 icon-radix">
                                    <path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                        </h3>
                        <div data-state="closed" id="radix-3" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-button-3"
                            data-orientation="vertical" class="accordion-content text-sm">
                            <p class="py-4">제품 A는 기본 모델이며, 제품 B는 추가 기능이 포함된 모델입니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b">
                        <h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex">
                            <button type="button" aria-controls="radix-4" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"
                                data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-button-4"
                                class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between py-4 transition-all hover:underline text-base font-medium"
                                onclick="toggleAccordion('radix-4')">
                                주문 취소 및 변경은 어떻게 하나요?
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200 icon-radix">
                                    <path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                        </h3>
                        <div data-state="closed" id="radix-4" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-button-4"
                            data-orientation="vertical" class="accordion-content text-sm">
                            <p class="py-4">주문 취소 및 변경은 주문 후 24시간 이내에 가능합니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b">
                        <h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex">
                            <button type="button" aria-controls="radix-5" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"
                                data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-button-5"
                                class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between py-4 transition-all hover:underline text-base font-medium"
                                onclick="toggleAccordion('radix-5')">
                                제품 A의 A/S는 어떻게 받을 수 있나요?
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200 icon-radix">
                                    <path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                        </h3>
                        <div data-state="closed" id="radix-5" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-button-5"
                            data-orientation="vertical" class="accordion-content text-sm">
                            <p class="py-4">제품 A의 A/S는 고객 지원 센터에 문의하여 받을 수 있습니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b">
                        <h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex">
                            <button type="button" aria-controls="radix-6" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"
                                data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-button-6"
                                class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between py-4 transition-all hover:underline text-base font-medium"
                                onclick="toggleAccordion('radix-6')">
                                항목 제목을 입력하세요
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                                    stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200 icon-radix">
                                    <path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                        </h3>
                        <div data-state="closed" id="radix-6" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-button-6"
                            data-orientation="vertical" class="accordion-content text-sm">
                            <p class="py-4">항목 내용을 입력하세요.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        function toggleAccordion(id) {
            const content = document.getElementById(id);
            const button = document.querySelector(`button[aria-controls="${id}"]`);
            const isOpen = content.getAttribute('data-state') === 'open';

            if (isOpen) {
                content.style.maxHeight = '0';
                button.querySelector('svg').classList.remove('icon-open');
                button.querySelector('svg').classList.add('icon-radix');
            } else {
                content.style.maxHeight = content.scrollHeight + 'px';
                button.querySelector('svg').classList.remove('icon-radix');
                button.querySelector('svg').classList.add('icon-open');
            }

            content.setAttribute('data-state', isOpen ? 'closed' : 'open');
            button.setAttribute('aria-expanded', !isOpen);
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>